c: 17
v: 12
t: "Thina Sibeke ubusuku nemini ukuba zibe yimiqondiso emibini, Saza kananjalo Sawenza waba mnyama umqondiso wobusuku lo gama Senze umqondiso wemini waba kukukhanya, khon’ukuze nikwazi ukufuna iziBele eNkosini yenu, kwanokuba nikwazi ukubala inani leminyaka nokuba nomqaphela (wezinto). Ke kaloku Sinichazele yonke into ngengcaciso egcweleyo"